7. Pantheon Interpretation

This invariant is the epistemic foundation of the Pantheon stack.

Spider

Tracks mappings and transformations:
	•	X -> X1 -> X2 -> X3

Mirror

Checks whether meaningful invariants are actually preserved:
	•	Is this the same structure or just decorative similarity?

Checksum

Records provenance and verifies continuity:
	•	Did the thing actually persist, or are we confabulating continuity?

Hound

Detects false positives:
	•	patterns that feel persistent but are just repeated noise or emotional stickiness

Mother Duck

Stores and organizes the surviving artifacts in continuity space

